				<div class="vote-text col-md-10 hidden">
				<h4>Lost Local Brewing</h4>
				<p>Trubbel</p>
				<p>Belgian Dark Strong ABV: 8.9%</p>
				<ul>Awards:
					<li>Motown MASH (NJ, BJCP Sanctioned: 1ST Place Belgian Strong2</li>
					<li>Old Forge Old Ale Competition (NY, BJCP Sanctioned): 1st Place Belgian and Best of Show</li>
